      </memberdef>
    </sectiondef>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Use <ref refid="structqristal_1_1NoiseProperties" kindref="compound">NoiseProperties</ref> to accept user input parameters for custom noise models. There are 3 types of inputs used for constructing a custom noise model: </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Qubit topology</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Time duration of quantum gate operations</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Parameters for quantum noise channels and classical errors </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
